      "rdf:value": "<L>181<pc>0009-b<k1>aga<k2>aga\n{#aga#}¦ {%<ab>a.</ab>%} [{#na gacCatIti; gam-qa#}. {#na#}. {#ta#}].\n{@1@} Unable to walk, not going, not\nin a position to go; {#ago vfzalaH SItena#}\n<ls>P. VI. 3. 77</ls> <ls>Sk.</ls> {@--2@} <lbinfo n=\"Unapproach+able\"/>\nUnapproachable. {#--gaH#} {@1@} A tree; {#sadAnato yena#} <lbinfo n=\"vizARi#nA\"/>\n{#vizARinA'gaH#} <ls>Śi. 4. 63.</ls> {@--2@} A mountain; also\na stone; {#pratyApagaM pratyagaM#} <ls>Mahānāṭaka.</ls>\n{@--3@} A snake. {@--4@} The sun ({#na#} <lbinfo n=\"gacCa#ti\"/>\n{#gacCati vakragatyA paScimaM, tasya hi vakragatyaBAvo#} <lbinfo n=\"jyo#tizaprasidDaH\"/>\n{#jyotizaprasidDaH#}; or, ‘not going’, the earth by\nits diurnal rotation causing day and\nnight). {@--5@} A water-jar, as in {#agastya#}\n({#kuMBastyAna#}). {@--6@} The number seven (from\nthe seven {#kulAcala#}s). {@--Comp.@}  <lbinfo n=\"--A#tmajA\"/>\n{#--AtmajA#} the daughter of the mountain,\n<ab>N.</ab> of Pārvatī. {#--okas#} {%<ab>m.</ab>%} [{#agaH#} <lbinfo n=\"parva#taH\"/>\n{#parvataH oko yasya#}] {1} a <lbinfo n=\"mountain-dwell+er\"/>\nmountain-dweller. {2} a bird ({#vfkzavAsI#}). {3} the <lbinfo n=\"ani+mal\"/>\nanimal {#SaraBa#} supposed to have 8 legs. {4}\na lion. {#--ja#} {%<ab>a.</ab>%} ({#agAt parvataSilAto#} <lbinfo n=\"jA#yate\"/>\n{#jAyate; jaR-qa#}.) produced on a <lbinfo n=\"moun+tain\"/>\nmountain or from a tree; roaming or <lbinfo n=\"wan+dering\"/>\nwandering through mountains, wild\n({#giricara#}); {#kacAcitO vizvagivAgajO gajO#}\n<ls>Ki. 1. 36.</ls> {#--(jaM)#} bitumen.\n<LEND>"
